  <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
  <p>
    KickWiz is an AFL match analytics and prediction tool. The App uses statistical models and a
    five-agent AI ensemble to generate match predictions, player analysis, and team comparisons for
    educational and entertainment purposes.
  </p>
  <p>
