  </p>

  <h2>4. Access and Subscription</h2>
  <p>
    Access to KickWiz requires an active auto-renewing subscription. <strong>There is no free version of
    the App and no free tier of features.</strong> Every feature is available to subscribers and to users
    in the free trial period.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Free trial</strong>: New users receive a 5-day free trial. You may cancel at any point during the trial without being billed.</li>
    <li><strong>Price</strong>: A$29.99 per month, billed monthly to your Apple ID.</li>
    <li><strong>Renewal</strong>: The subscription renews automatically each month unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.</li>
    <li><strong>Cancellation</strong>: Manage or cancel your subscription via Settings &gt; Apple ID &gt; Subscriptions on your device. KickWiz cannot cancel a subscription on your behalf.</li>
    <li><strong>Refunds</strong>: Refunds are handled by Apple under the App Store Terms of Service. KickWiz does not process refunds directly.</li>
    <li><strong>No account required</strong>: KickWiz has no sign-up, sign-in, or login of any kind. Access is granted automatically once your subscription or trial is active, by reading entitlements from Apple StoreKit.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Payment processing is handled entirely by Apple. KickWiz does not collect or store payment
    information.
  </p>

